sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Browser
  participant N as Nginx
  participant G as Gateway
  participant R as Rule Engine
  participant S as Scheduler
  participant K as K8s Job

  B->>N: GET /labs/edu.hot.zk-modular
  N->>B: dist/index.html + JS

  B->>N: POST /api/v1/labs/.../simulate
  N->>G: proxy
  G->>R: POST /evaluate
  R-->>G: evaluation + audit_hints
  G-->>B: JSON

  Note over B,S: 用户点击提交 Job（cluster 模式）
  B->>G: POST simulate taskType=...
  G->>S: POST /submit
  S->>K: create Job
  K-->>S: Pod completed
  S-->>G: report
  G-->>B: task status
